            "title": "台股回吐0.82%收市",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">台股連日創新高後，今日先行回吐。台灣加權指數高開低走，收報32536點，跌267點或0.82%。</p>\n</div>",
