            "title": "內地A股早市陷爭持 青島銀行漲停板",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">內地股市今早再現爭持局面，深市相對跑贏；貴金屬板塊仍受捧，青島銀行(03866)A股(002948.SZ)發業績快報後更漲停板。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"青島銀行官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/09/03866-Web.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"青島銀行官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/09/03866-Web.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">青島銀行官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">上證綜指今早高開4點後反覆偏軟，初段最高僅報4157點，升6點，早市中段低位見4138點，倒跌12點，後段陷入爭持；滬指中午收報4147點，跌4點或0.1%，半日成交9042.04億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">深證成指低開10點後初段跌幅曾略為擴大至56點，跌至14286點便反彈，早市大部份時間報升，最高報14418點，升75點；深指中午收報14344點，升2點或0.01%，成交1.11萬億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滬深300指數則跌4點或0.1%，收報4713點；創業板指數跌1點或0.05%，報3322點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-1.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-1.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">青島銀行昨天收市後發業績快報，顯示去年純利按年升21.66%；青島銀行A股今早裂口跳升，於早市後段升近10%封板，收報5.09元。個別中小銀行股亦跟升，渝農商行(03618)A股(601077.SH)便升2.58%，報6.37元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">貴金屬價格高踞不下，相關股份繼續受捧。江西銅業(00358)A股(600362.SH)升6.7%，報68.63元；中國鋁業(02600)A股(601600.SH)升5.14%，報15.35元。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/20230725_FI_source-web_00358_FB.jpg.webp\">\n<img src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/20230725_FI_source-web_00358_FB.jpg.webp\"/>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">赤峰黃金(06693)A股(600988.SH)4.55 %，報48.99元；山東黃金(01787)A股(600547.SH)升3.89%，報61.98元；紫金礦業(02899)A股(601899.SH)升3%，報43.57元；洛陽鉬業(03993)A股(603993.SH)升2.98%，報27.68元。</p>\n</div>",
